data.description: Welcome to your serene retreat in the heart of a vibrant 55+ community! This stunning 2-bedroom plus den condo, situated on the second floor, offers a perfect blend of tranquility and luxury living.  As you step inside, you'll immediately be captivated by the breathtaking views of trees and lush green space, creating an ambiance of peace and relaxation. The highlight of this home is the extra-large glass-enclosed patio, where you can bask in the beauty of nature while enjoying the fresh air. With screens installed, you have the flexibility to open the windows and let the gentle breeze flow through, enhancing your indoor-outdoor living experience.  Step inside and discover a haven of luxury and comfort, with exquisite solid surface flooring that exudes elegance and durability. The home boasts a range of luxury updates, including a newer HVAC system to ensure year-round comfort, a remodeled kitchen adorned with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and updated lighting fixtures. Every detail has been carefully curated to elevate your living experience, with designer touches adding a touch of sophistication to every corner.  Retreat to the spacious primary bedroom where you'll find  large closests with  custom organizers,  and a beautifully tiled shower, updated vanity, and lighting in the ensuite bathroom, creating a spa-like atmosphere for your daily relaxation rituals.  This move-in-ready home not only offers unparalleled comfort and style but also grants you access to a plethora of community amenities, too numerous to mention. From recreational facilities to social gatherings, there's something for everyone in this vibrant 55+ community.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home and embrace the ultimate in luxury living combined with the tranquility of a natural setting. Schedule your viewing today and experience the epitome of 55+ living at its finest!
